      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are hotlines, but they don't understand how this actually feels. they just give me scripts. they don't understand that the debt is permanent and the failure is permanent. talkin to a stranger on the phone doesn't fix the fact that i've ruined my family's name. it's like... if you have an unsolvable problem, why keep trying to solve it? it's just exhausting to keep breathing when everything is broken.",
